nIstructions and Specifications of how to compile, 
install and execute the PSO implementation and configure the robot swarm controller:
=====================================================================================================

- the language used is Python3 so just install python3 and the following libraries : 

    - required python Libraries : 
        - time
        - math
        - threading
        - csv
        - random
        - datetime
        - ranksums from scipy.stats
        - subprocess
        - shlex

        
=====================================================================================================
- to run the PSO : 

    - first manually set the random seeds in the 10 different decision-making{i}.argos where i is between 1 and 10
    
    - change the seeds in the main() function of main.py
    
    - then, run "python3 main.py" in terminal
    
- The results are shown in terminal and the csv + boxplots files are created in the "Results" file



